We found South Africa’s very own chocolate bae!  Chocolatier Jermaine van Zyl of Huguenot Fine Chocolates in Franschhoek will get your taste buds in all sorts with his sweet skills on how to create the best chocolate truffles this side of the equator. If you plan on going for Bastille Day or are in the vicinity of Franschhoek do yourself a favour and experience the chocolate-making skills of Chocolate Bae at Huguenot Fine Chocolates. Watch the video below for a taste of the chocolate experience: 